     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap mappingSystemeFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-mappingSystemeFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcmappingSystemeFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-systeme</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-assigned-author</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.identifiantAuteur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.professionSavoirFaireRole</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.systeme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.assignedAuthoringDevice</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.systeme.nomModeleSysteme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.assignedAuthoringDevice.manufacturerModelName</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.systeme.nomSysteme</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.assignedAuthoringDevice.softwareName</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.structure</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.representedOrganization</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.structure.identifiantStructure</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.representedOrganization.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.structure.nomStructure</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.representedOrganization.name</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.structure.adresse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.representedOrganization.addr</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSysteme.identificationAuteur.structure.coordonneesTelecom</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>assignedAuthor.representedOrganization.telecom</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-assigned-author</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-device-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>assignedAuthor</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a>